author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be a pretty unethical experiment where a University launched AI bots on r/changemyview. These bots attempted to change minds and pretended to be humans and no one knew until it was all done and over with. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: The Worst Experiment On Reddit Just Happened...
